The paper proposes a method for image retrieval using deep neural network activations and local feature matching. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The method also involves robust matching and optimization, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the paper does not involve any modification or training of the neural network, which could fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
